<hw>Mea"gre</hw> }</mhw>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<def>To make lean.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>meagerly</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Meagre
<hw>Mea"gre</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>maigre</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A large European
sciaenoid fish (<spn>Sciaena umbra</spn> or <spn>Sciaena aquila</spn>),
having white bloodless flesh. It is valued as a food fish.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>maigre</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Meak</ent>⟦br⟧
